FBIS4-7138 "dreas082_c_94020" FBIS-EAS-94-082 Daily Report 23 Apr 1994 North Korea Further on Celebration of Kim Il-song Birthday Further on Celebration of Kim Il-song Birthday Work Published in Portugal SK2304111894 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1044 GMT 23 Apr 94 SK2304111894 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 23 (KCNA) -- The great leader President Kim Il-song's famous work "Enhancing the Role of the Popular Masses is the Guarantee for Victory in the Cause of Independence" was published in booklet by the Grafica Europa publishing house of Portugal, on the occasion of his birthday. The preface of the booklet says: President Kim Il-song of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea is recognised by the world people as the leader who has adorned the current century with unheard of great traces which will remain in the history of mankind. President Kim Il-song is respected by the entire Korean people as well as hundreds of millions of people all over the world as he has devoted his 80 odd years to the people as their son.
